These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
City: new-york, boston, paris, colone
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| City   | paris | boston | new-york | colone |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, boat, trike, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Transport   | helicopter | trike | boat | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, r&b, classical, techno
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Music-Genre   | classical | blues | r&b | techno |

 #################################

 
