2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |
| Birthday   | march | february | april | july |

